            <div class="d-flex sub">
              <div><i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up"></i></div> 
              <p>Give visitors confidence via higher transparency</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex sub">
              <div><i class="bi bi-megaphone"></i></div> 
              <p>Brand building as your links circulate around the web</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex sub">
              <div><i class="bi bi-people"></i></div> 
